{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This is Tim Ferriss circa 1979 A.D. Age two."},{"time":6000,"text":"You can tell by the power squat, I was a very confident boy --"},{"time":9000,"text":"and not without reason."},{"time":11000,"text":"I had a very charming routine at the time,"},{"time":13000,"text":"which was to wait until late in the evening"},{"time":15000,"text":"when my parents were decompressing from a hard day's work,"},{"time":18000,"text":"doing their crossword puzzles, watching television."},{"time":20000,"text":"I would run into the living room, jump up on the couch,"},{"time":23000,"text":"rip the cushions off, throw them on the floor,"},{"time":25000,"text":"scream at the top of my lungs and run out"},{"time":27000,"text":"because I was the Incredible Hulk."},{"time":29000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":31000,"text":"Obviously, you see the resemblance."},{"time":33000,"text":"And this routine went on for some time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"When I was seven I went to summer camp."},{"time":40000,"text":"My parents found it necessary for peace of mind."},{"time":42000,"text":"And at noon each day"},{"time":44000,"text":"the campers would go to a pond,"},{"time":46000,"text":"where they had floating docks."},{"time":48000,"text":"You could jump off the end into the deep end."},{"time":50000,"text":"I was born premature. I was always very small."},{"time":52000,"text":"My left lung had collapsed when I was born."},{"time":54000,"text":"And I've always had buoyancy problems."},{"time":56000,"text":"So water was something that scared me to begin with."},{"time":58000,"text":"But I would go in on occasion."},{"time":60000,"text":"And on one particular day,"},{"time":62000,"text":"the campers were jumping through inner tubes,"},{"time":65000,"text":"They were diving through inner tubes. And I thought this would be great fun."},{"time":67000,"text":"So I dove through the inner tube,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and the bully of the camp grabbed my ankles."},{"time":72000,"text":"And I tried to come up for air,"},{"time":76000,"text":"and my lower back hit the bottom of the inner tube."},{"time":78000,"text":"And I went wild eyed and thought I was going to die."},{"time":82000,"text":"A camp counselor fortunately came over and separated us."},{"time":85000,"text":"From that point onward I was terrified of swimming."},{"time":89000,"text":"That is something that I did not get over."},{"time":92000,"text":"My inability to swim has been"},{"time":94000,"text":"one of my greatest humiliations and embarrassments."},{"time":99000,"text":"That is when I realized that I was not the Incredible Hulk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"But there is a happy ending to this story."},{"time":105000,"text":"At age 31 -- that's my age now --"},{"time":109000,"text":"in August I took two weeks to re-examine swimming,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and question all the of the obvious aspects of swimming."},{"time":117000,"text":"And went from swimming one lap --"},{"time":119000,"text":"so 20 yards -- like a drowning monkey,"},{"time":121000,"text":"at about 200 beats per minute heart rate --"},{"time":123000,"text":"I measured it --"},{"time":125000,"text":"to going to Montauk on Long Island,"},{"time":128000,"text":"close to where I grew up,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and jumping into the ocean and swimming one kilometer in open water,"},{"time":133000,"text":"getting out and feeling better than when I went in."},{"time":135000,"text":"And I came out,"},{"time":137000,"text":"in my Speedos, European style,"},{"time":140000,"text":"feeling like the Incredible Hulk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"And that's what I want everyone in here to feel like,"},{"time":144000,"text":"the Incredible Hulk, at the end of this presentation."},{"time":147000,"text":"More specifically, I want you to feel like you're capable"},{"time":149000,"text":"of becoming an excellent long-distance swimmer,"},{"time":153000,"text":"a world-class language learner,"},{"time":155000,"text":"and a tango champion."},{"time":158000,"text":"And I would like to share my art."},{"time":161000,"text":"If I have an art, it's deconstructing things"},{"time":163000,"text":"that really scare the living hell out of me."},{"time":165000,"text":"So, moving onward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"Swimming, first principles."},{"time":169000,"text":"First principles, this is very important."},{"time":171000,"text":"I find that the best results in life"},{"time":173000,"text":"are often held back by false constructs and untested assumptions."},{"time":178000,"text":"And the turnaround in swimming came"},{"time":180000,"text":"when a friend of mine said, \"I will go a year without any stimulants\" --"},{"time":183000,"text":"this is a six-double-espresso-per-day type of guy --"},{"time":186000,"text":"\"if you can complete a one kilometer open water race.\""},{"time":189000,"text":"So the clock started ticking."},{"time":191000,"text":"I started seeking out triathletes"},{"time":193000,"text":"because I found that lifelong swimmers often couldn't teach what they did."},{"time":197000,"text":"I tried kickboards."},{"time":200000,"text":"My feet would slice through the water like razors,"},{"time":202000,"text":"I wouldn't even move. I would leave demoralized, staring at my feet."},{"time":205000,"text":"Hand paddles, everything."},{"time":207000,"text":"Even did lessons with Olympians -- nothing helped."},{"time":210000,"text":"And then Chris Sacca, who is now a dear friend mine,"},{"time":212000,"text":"had completed an Iron Man with 103 degree temperature,"},{"time":215000,"text":"said, \"I have the answer to your prayers.\""},{"time":217000,"text":"And he introduced me to"},{"time":219000,"text":"the work of a man named Terry Laughlin"},{"time":221000,"text":"who is the founder of Total Immersion Swimming."},{"time":223000,"text":"That set me on the road to examining biomechanics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"So here are the new rules of swimming,"},{"time":228000,"text":"if any of you are afraid of swimming, or not good at it."},{"time":231000,"text":"The first is, forget about kicking. Very counterintuitive."},{"time":234000,"text":"So it turns out that propulsion isn't really the problem."},{"time":238000,"text":"Kicking harder doesn't solve the problem"},{"time":240000,"text":"because the average swimmer only transfers about three percent"},{"time":243000,"text":"of their energy expenditure into forward motion."},{"time":246000,"text":"The problem is hydrodynamics."},{"time":248000,"text":"So what you want to focus on instead"},{"time":250000,"text":"is allowing your lower body to draft behind your upper body,"},{"time":252000,"text":"much like a small car behind a big car on the highway."},{"time":255000,"text":"And you do that by maintaining a horizontal body position."},{"time":258000,"text":"The only way you can do that"},{"time":260000,"text":"is to not swim on top of the water."},{"time":262000,"text":"The body is denser than water. 95 percent of it would be,"},{"time":265000,"text":"at least, submerged naturally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"So you end up, number three,"},{"time":269000,"text":"not swimming, in the case of freestyle,"},{"time":272000,"text":"on your stomach, as many people think, reaching on top of the water."},{"time":275000,"text":"But actually rotating from streamlined right"},{"time":278000,"text":"to streamlined left,"},{"time":280000,"text":"maintaining that fuselage position as long as possible."},{"time":283000,"text":"So let's look at some examples. This is Terry."},{"time":285000,"text":"And you can see that he's extending his right arm"},{"time":288000,"text":"below his head and far in front."},{"time":290000,"text":"And so his entire body really is underwater."},{"time":293000,"text":"The arm is extended below the head."},{"time":296000,"text":"The head is held in line with the spine,"},{"time":298000,"text":"so that you use strategic water pressure to raise your legs up --"},{"time":302000,"text":"very important, especially for people with lower body fat."},{"time":305000,"text":"Here is an example of the stroke."},{"time":307000,"text":"So you don't kick. But you do use a small flick."},{"time":310000,"text":"You can see this is the left extension."},{"time":312000,"text":"Then you see his left leg."},{"time":314000,"text":"Small flick, and the only purpose of that"},{"time":316000,"text":"is to rotate his hips so he can get to the opposite side."},{"time":319000,"text":"And the entry point for his right hand -- notice this,"},{"time":321000,"text":"he's not reaching in front and catching the water."},{"time":323000,"text":"Rather, he is entering the water"},{"time":326000,"text":"at a 45-degree angle with his forearm,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and then propelling himself by streamlining -- very important."},{"time":334000,"text":"Incorrect, above, which is what almost every swimming coach will teach you."},{"time":337000,"text":"Not their fault, honestly."},{"time":339000,"text":"And I'll get to implicit versus explicit in a moment."},{"time":342000,"text":"Below is what most swimmers"},{"time":344000,"text":"will find enables them to do what I did,"},{"time":346000,"text":"which is going from 21 strokes per 20-yard length"},{"time":350000,"text":"to 11 strokes"},{"time":353000,"text":"in two workouts with no coach, no video monitoring."},{"time":356000,"text":"And now I love swimming. I can't wait to go swimming."},{"time":359000,"text":"I'll be doing a swimming lesson later, for myself, if anyone wants to join me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363000,"text":"Last thing, breathing. A problem a lot of us have, certainly, when you're swimming."},{"time":367000,"text":"In freestyle, easiest way to remedy this is"},{"time":369000,"text":"to turn with body roll,"},{"time":372000,"text":"and just to look at your recovery hand as it enters the water."},{"time":376000,"text":"And that will get you very far."},{"time":379000,"text":"That's it. That's really all you need to know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382000,"text":"Languages. Material versus method."},{"time":384000,"text":"I, like many people, came to the conclusion"},{"time":386000,"text":"that I was terrible at languages."},{"time":388000,"text":"I suffered through Spanish for junior high, first year of high school,"},{"time":392000,"text":"and the sum total of my knowledge"},{"time":394000,"text":"was pretty much, \"Donde esta el bano?\""},{"time":396000,"text":"And I wouldn't even catch the response. A sad state of affairs."},{"time":401000,"text":"Then I transferred to a different school sophomore year, and"},{"time":405000,"text":"I had a choice of other languages. Most of my friends were taking Japanese."},{"time":407000,"text":"So I thought why not punish myself? I'll do Japanese."},{"time":411000,"text":"Six months later I had the chance to go to Japan."},{"time":414000,"text":"My teachers assured me, they said, \"Don't worry."},{"time":416000,"text":"You'll have Japanese language classes every day to help you cope."},{"time":420000,"text":"It will be an amazing experience.\" My first overseas experience in fact."},{"time":424000,"text":"So my parents encouraged me to do it. I left."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"I arrived in Tokyo. Amazing."},{"time":429000,"text":"I couldn't believe I was on the other side of the world."},{"time":431000,"text":"I met my host family. Things went quite well I think,"},{"time":433000,"text":"all things considered."},{"time":435000,"text":"My first evening, before my first day of school,"},{"time":438000,"text":"I said to my mother, very politely,"},{"time":440000,"text":"\"Please wake me up at eight a.m.\""},{"time":442000,"text":"So, (Japanese)"},{"time":444000,"text":"But I didn't say (Japanese). I said, (Japanese). Pretty close."},{"time":448000,"text":"But I said, \"Please rape me at eight a.m.\""},{"time":451000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":454000,"text":"You've never seen a more confused Japanese woman."},{"time":456000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":460000,"text":"I walked in to school."},{"time":462000,"text":"And a teacher came up to me and handed me a piece of paper."},{"time":465000,"text":"I couldn't read any of it -- hieroglyphics, it could have been --"},{"time":468000,"text":"because it was Kanji,"},{"time":470000,"text":"Chinese characters adapted into the Japanese language."},{"time":472000,"text":"Asked him what this said."},{"time":474000,"text":"And he goes, \"Ahh, okay okay,"},{"time":476000,"text":"eehto, World History, ehh, Calculus,"},{"time":480000,"text":"Traditional Japanese.\" And so on."},{"time":484000,"text":"And so it came to me in waves."},{"time":487000,"text":"There had been something lost in translation."},{"time":490000,"text":"The Japanese classes were not Japanese instruction classes, per se."},{"time":493000,"text":"They were the normal high school curriculum for Japanese students --"},{"time":497000,"text":"the other 4,999 students in the school, who were Japanese, besides the American."},{"time":501000,"text":"And that's pretty much my response."},{"time":504000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":505000,"text":"And that set me on this panic driven search for the perfect language method."},{"time":510000,"text":"I tried everything. I went to Kinokuniya."},{"time":512000,"text":"I tried every possible book, every possible CD."},{"time":515000,"text":"Nothing worked until I found this."},{"time":517000,"text":"This is the Joyo Kanji. This is a Tablet rather,"},{"time":521000,"text":"or a poster of the 1,945 common-use characters"},{"time":525000,"text":"as determined by the Ministry of Education in 1981."},{"time":528000,"text":"Many of the publications in Japan limit themselves to these characters,"},{"time":532000,"text":"to facilitate literacy -- some are required to."},{"time":534000,"text":"And this became my Holy Grail, my Rosetta Stone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"As soon as I focused on this material,"},{"time":542000,"text":"I took off."},{"time":544000,"text":"I ended up being able to read Asahi Shinbu, Asahi newspaper,"},{"time":547000,"text":"about six months later -- so a total of 11 months later --"},{"time":550000,"text":"and went from Japanese I to Japanese VI."},{"time":552000,"text":"Ended up doing translation work at age 16 when I returned to the U.S.,"},{"time":555000,"text":"and have continued to apply this material"},{"time":560000,"text":"over method approach to close to a dozen languages now."},{"time":563000,"text":"Someone who was terrible at languages,"},{"time":565000,"text":"and at any given time, speak, read and write five or six."},{"time":570000,"text":"This brings us to the point,"},{"time":572000,"text":"which is, it's oftentimes what you do,"},{"time":575000,"text":"not how you do it, that is the determining factor."},{"time":578000,"text":"This is the difference between being effective -- doing the right things --"},{"time":581000,"text":"and being efficient -- doing things well whether or not they're important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584000,"text":"You can also do this with grammar."},{"time":586000,"text":"I came up with these six sentences after much experimentation."},{"time":590000,"text":"Having a native speaker allow you to deconstruct their grammar,"},{"time":593000,"text":"by translating these sentences into past, present, future,"},{"time":596000,"text":"will show you subject, object, verb,"},{"time":598000,"text":"placement of indirect, direct objects, gender and so forth."},{"time":600000,"text":"From that point, you can then, if you want to,"},{"time":603000,"text":"acquire multiple languages, alternate them so there is no interference."},{"time":605000,"text":"We can talk about that if anyone in interested."},{"time":608000,"text":"And now I love languages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610000,"text":"So ballroom dancing, implicit versus explicit --"},{"time":613000,"text":"very important."},{"time":614000,"text":"You might look at me and say, \"That guy must be a ballroom dancer.\""},{"time":617000,"text":"But no, you'd be wrong"},{"time":619000,"text":"because my body is very poorly designed for most things --"},{"time":622000,"text":"pretty well designed for lifting heavy rocks perhaps."},{"time":625000,"text":"I used to be much bigger, much more muscular."},{"time":628000,"text":"And so I ended up walking like this."},{"time":630000,"text":"I looked a lot like an orangutan, our close cousins, or the Incredible Hulk."},{"time":636000,"text":"Not very good for ballroom dancing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638000,"text":"I found myself in Argentina in 2005,"},{"time":641000,"text":"decided to watch a tango class -- had no intention of participating."},{"time":644000,"text":"Went in, paid my ten pesos,"},{"time":646000,"text":"walked up -- 10 women two guys, usually a good ratio."},{"time":649000,"text":"The instructor says, \"You are participating.\""},{"time":652000,"text":"Immediately: death sweat."},{"time":654000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":655000,"text":"Fight-or-flight fear sweat, because I tried ballroom dancing in college --"},{"time":658000,"text":"stepped on the girl's foot with my heel. She screamed."},{"time":661000,"text":"I was so concerned with her perception of what I was doing,"},{"time":664000,"text":"that it exploded in my face,"},{"time":666000,"text":"never to return to the ballroom dancing club."},{"time":669000,"text":"She comes up, and this was her approach, the teacher."},{"time":672000,"text":"\"Okay, come on, grab me.\""},{"time":674000,"text":"Gorgeous assistant instructor."},{"time":676000,"text":"She was very pissed off that I had pulled her from her advanced practice."},{"time":679000,"text":"So I did my best. I didn't know where to put my hands."},{"time":682000,"text":"And she pulled back, threw down her arms,"},{"time":684000,"text":"put them on her hips, turned around and yelled across the room,"},{"time":687000,"text":"\"This guy is built like a god-damned mountain of muscle,"},{"time":691000,"text":"and he's grabbing me like a fucking Frenchman,\""},{"time":693000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":695000,"text":"which I found encouraging."},{"time":697000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":699000,"text":"Everyone burst into laughter. I was humiliated."},{"time":701000,"text":"She came back. She goes, \"Come on. I don't have all day.\""},{"time":704000,"text":"As someone who wrestled since age eight, I proceeded to crush her,"},{"time":707000,"text":"\"Of Mice and Men\" style."},{"time":709000,"text":"And she looked up and said,"},{"time":711000,"text":"\"Now that's better.\""},{"time":714000,"text":"So I bought a month's worth of classes."},{"time":716000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":717000,"text":"And proceeded to look at --"},{"time":719000,"text":"I wanted to set competition so I'd have a deadline --"},{"time":721000,"text":"Parkinson's Law,"},{"time":723000,"text":"the perceived complexity of a task will expand to fill the time you allot it."},{"time":727000,"text":"So I had a very short deadline for a competition."},{"time":730000,"text":"I got a female instructor first,"},{"time":733000,"text":"to teach me the female role, the follow,"},{"time":736000,"text":"because I wanted to understand the sensitivities and abilities"},{"time":738000,"text":"that the follow needed to develop, so I wouldn't have a repeat of college."},{"time":741000,"text":"And then I took an inventory of the characteristics,"},{"time":744000,"text":"along with her, of the"},{"time":748000,"text":"of the capabilities and elements of different dancers who'd won championships."},{"time":751000,"text":"I interviewed these people because they all taught in Buenos Aires."},{"time":755000,"text":"I compared the two lists,"},{"time":757000,"text":"and what you find is that there is explicitly,"},{"time":759000,"text":"expertise they recommended, certain training methods."},{"time":762000,"text":"Then there were implicit commonalities"},{"time":764000,"text":"that none of them seemed to be practicing."},{"time":767000,"text":"Now the protectionism of Argentine dance teachers aside,"},{"time":770000,"text":"I found this very interesting. So I decided to focus on three of those commonalities."},{"time":774000,"text":"Long steps. So a lot of milongueros --"},{"time":776000,"text":"the tango dancers will use very short steps."},{"time":780000,"text":"I found that longer steps were much more elegant."},{"time":784000,"text":"So you can have --"},{"time":786000,"text":"and you can do it in a very small space in fact."},{"time":788000,"text":"Secondly, different types of pivots."},{"time":791000,"text":"Thirdly, variation in tempo."},{"time":794000,"text":"These seemed to be the three areas that I could exploit to compete"},{"time":797000,"text":"if I wanted to comptete against people who'd been practicing for 20 to 30 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801000,"text":"That photo is of the"},{"time":804000,"text":"semi-finals of the Buenos Aires championships, four months later."},{"time":807000,"text":"Then one month later, went to the world championships,"},{"time":810000,"text":"made it to the semi-final. And then set a world record, following that,"},{"time":812000,"text":"two weeks later."},{"time":813000,"text":"I want you to see part of what I practiced."},{"time":816000,"text":"I'm going to jump forward here."},{"time":819000,"text":"This is the instructor that Alicia and I chose for the male lead."},{"time":824000,"text":"His name is Gabriel Misse."},{"time":826000,"text":"One of the most elegant dancers of his generation,"},{"time":830000,"text":"known for his long steps, and his tempo changes"},{"time":832000,"text":"and his pivots."},{"time":837000,"text":"Alicia, in her own right, very famous."},{"time":839000,"text":"So I think you'll agree, they look quite good together."},{"time":844000,"text":"Now what I like about this video"},{"time":847000,"text":"is it's actually a video of the first time they ever danced together"},{"time":849000,"text":"because of his lead. He had a strong lead."},{"time":852000,"text":"He didn't lead with his chest, which requires you lean forward."},{"time":854000,"text":"I couldn't develop the attributes in my toes,"},{"time":856000,"text":"the strength in my feet, to do that."},{"time":859000,"text":"So he uses a lead that focuses on"},{"time":862000,"text":"his shoulder girdle and his arm."},{"time":865000,"text":"So he can lift the woman to break her, for example."},{"time":867000,"text":"That's just one benefit of that."},{"time":869000,"text":"So then we broke it down."},{"time":873000,"text":"This would be an example of one pivot."},{"time":875000,"text":"This is a back step pivot."},{"time":877000,"text":"There are many different types."},{"time":879000,"text":"I have hundreds of hours of footage --"},{"time":882000,"text":"all categorized, much like George Carlin"},{"time":884000,"text":"categorized his comedy."},{"time":890000,"text":"So using my arch-nemesis,"},{"time":892000,"text":"Spanish, no less, to learn tango."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894000,"text":"So fear is your friend. Fear is an indicator."},{"time":896000,"text":"Sometimes it shows you what you shouldn't do."},{"time":898000,"text":"More often than not it shows you exactly what you should do."},{"time":901000,"text":"And the best results that I've had in life,"},{"time":903000,"text":"the most enjoyable times, have all been from asking a simple question:"},{"time":906000,"text":"what's the worst that can happen?"},{"time":908000,"text":"Especially with fears you gained when you were a child."},{"time":912000,"text":"Take the analytical frameworks,"},{"time":915000,"text":"the capabilities you have, apply them to old fears."},{"time":917000,"text":"Apply them to very big dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":920000,"text":"And when I think of what I fear now, it's very simple."},{"time":923000,"text":"When I imagine my life,"},{"time":926000,"text":"what my life would have been like"},{"time":928000,"text":"without the educational opportunities that I had,"},{"time":932000,"text":"it makes me wonder."},{"time":934000,"text":"I've spent the last two years trying to deconstruct"},{"time":936000,"text":"the American public school system,"},{"time":939000,"text":"to either fix it or replace it."},{"time":941000,"text":"And have done experiments with about 50,000 students thus far --"},{"time":944000,"text":"built, I'd say, about a half dozen schools,"},{"time":946000,"text":"my readers, at this point."},{"time":948000,"text":"And if any of you are interested in that,"},{"time":950000,"text":"I would love to speak with you."},{"time":952000,"text":"I know nothing. I'm a beginner."},{"time":954000,"text":"But I ask a lot of questions, and I would love your advice."},{"time":957000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":959000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}